36 development project, as applicable, from any private not-for-
37 profit organization or local contributions from tax
38 abatement or other sources may be substituted on a dollar-
39 for-dollar basis for the local match of one hundred percent
40 of payments in lieu of taxes, [and] economic activity taxes,
41 and the municipal residential earnings tax increment from
42 the fund;
